    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors formally scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 at MRL 2 with medium model influence and Class II device classification. Output comparison confirms NIH prediction within 18% of in-vitro measurements across all five operating points, satisfying the 25% acceptance threshold. Discretization error GCI of 6.8% is below the 10% threshold. The model is assessed as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device.",
